## Fin Right — Fees & Service Details

| Slab | Fee |
|---|---|
| Flat fee | ₹5,900 to ₹50,000 |
| Percentage-based (for amounts ₹5L–₹50L+) | 1% of amount |

- Can assist with approximately **90% of the withdrawal process**.
- **Written agreement** includes refund policy — fee refunded if the claim fails (confirmed in writing).
- **₹500 registration fee** charged upfront — adjusted against final fee later.
- After registration, the **documentation team** will reach out.
- A **dedicated consultant** will be assigned to evaluate the fixes, assist with the entire process end-to-end, and **share the timeline**.
- **Minimum fee: ₹5,900 (incl. GST)** — covers everything (UAN merging, transfer, withdrawal, issue resolution). This is the minimum regardless of scope.

